        <h2>Culture</h2>
        <p>India's culture is an amalgamation of various customs, traditions, and beliefs. It is known for its diverse range of art forms, music, dance, and literature. The classical dance forms such as Bharatanatyam, Kathak, Odissi, and Kathakali showcase the rich artistic heritage of the country.</p>
