        <h2>Traditions</h2>
        <p>India is home to a variety of traditions that reflect its historical and cultural depth. Festivals like Diwali, Holi, and Eid are celebrated with immense zeal and are an integral part of the Indian lifestyle. Traditional attire such as sarees, turbans, and dhotis represent the diverse regional cultures.</p>
